Gg_CarPark

Made by The Giblets of Jesus

___________________________________ This map originally started out as a scenery test about 9 months ago after seeing something which caught my eye while I was traveling around Bournemouth (South-West England), a small car park with some foliage centered in the middle of it, with trees poking through the second level, and example of how people and architecture can adapt around nature, even inside a heavily urbanized area. Tl;Dr I saw some cool shit in a car park and made it into a test map :P Anyway, I dug this up recently and decided to make something of it by transforming it into a GunGame map. Gameplay is centered around the map's isometric, "figure of 8" design and features a good blend of long and medium ranged combat. ___________________________________

A few Features of this map:

+Constant, high FPS +HDR +90 Spawns (you can never have too many :P) +Volumetric lighting in spawn points +Isometric, "Figure of 8 design" design. ___________________________________

Like this map? Try the Gg_CarPark Menu Background :D
